&lt;div class="max-w-xl mx-auto"&gt;
    &lt;h1 class="text-2xl font-mono pb-4 "&gt;Manifest AI&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;div class="text-sm"&gt;
        &lt;p class="pb-2"&gt;
            What will AI be capable of tomorrow?
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p class="pb-2"&gt;
            We're building a foundational large language model featuring an infinite context window. Our breakthrough in AI training enhances understanding and processing capabilities, offering deeper, more insightful AI solutions across diverse industries.
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div class="flex flex-wrap pt-4 gap-2"&gt;
          &lt;a class="underline" href="mailto:jacob@manifestai.co"&gt;Get early access&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="pt-8"&gt;
        &lt;h2 class="font-mono text-lg flex justify-between pb-4 gap-1"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;ul class="pl-4 list-disc"&gt;
            &lt;li class="pb-2"&gt;What sets Manifest AI's model apart? Our model's infinite context window allows for unparalleled depth in understanding and response accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li class="pb-2"&gt;How does the infinite context window benefit users? It enables more precise and comprehensive responses, ideal for complex tasks and human-like interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li class="pb-2"&gt;What industries can use Manifest AI's technology? Various sectors including healthcare, finance, education, and customer service benefit from our deep data processing AI.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="pt-4"&gt;
        &lt;h2 class="font-mono text-lg flex justify-between"&gt;Recent Publications&lt;/h2&gt;
        {% for post in site.posts limit:5 %}
        &lt;a class="flex gap-1 items-center pt-4 underline hover:text-gray-600" href="{{ post.url }}"&gt;
            &lt;div&gt;{{ post.title }}&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/a&gt;
        {% endfor %}
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="pt-8"&gt;
        &lt;h2 class="font-mono text-lg flex justify-between pb-4 gap-1"&gt;Who are we?&lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;p class="pb-2"&gt; &lt;a class="underline" href="https://twitter.com/carlesgelada"&gt;Carles Gelada&lt;/a&gt; and  &lt;a class="underline" href="https://jacobbuckman.com/"&gt;Jacob Buckman&lt;/a&gt; are the co-founders who met at Google Brain, where they have been collaborating for over five years. Gelada, with significant contributions as a Research Scientist at OpenAI, has 1,300 citations to his name. Buckman, a PhD candidate at McGill University, complements this with 1,500 citations for his research. Their joint expertise continues to make waves in AI research.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

